<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/30826808-the-essential-ludwig-von-mises"><img alt="The Essential Ludwig von Mises" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1467414145l/30826808._SX98_.jpg" />
